I think I've stayed home too long.. Need some nature in the house.⁣
⁣
Inspired by @intotheplants & @onlychildsyndrome.gg. Bought a few pots of plants @rabbitislandsg to greenify the house. Hope they don't die under my hands after the CB.. 💗😂⁣
